The evidence with the title 'Addiction treatment with a Dark Side - the New York Times ' says Nov 16, 2013  ... Many buprenorphine doctors are addiction experts capable , they say, of treating far more than the federal limit of 100 patients . But because of that limit, an unmet demand for treatment has created a commercial opportunity for prescribers , attracting some with histories of overprescribing the very pain pills  ... 
